thread.title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Overseas Chinese Town says unit and investment firm to set up project company

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Shenzhen Overseas Chinese Town says unit and investment firm to set up project company

organizations.name: shenzhen overseas chinese town co ltd

text:
Jan 25 (Reuters) - Shenzhen Overseas Chinese Town Co Ltd :
* Says its property unit plans to set up a JV as project company, jointly with a Shenzhen-based investment firm
* JV will be capitalized at 100 million yuan and coâ€™s unit will own a 60 percent stake
* Says new project company will obtain development and operation rights of a Shenzhen-based property project
